[03:45.89]And as Prince Michael's eye rested upon the glowing face of the great clock in the tower, his smile, altruistic as it was, became slightly tinged with contempt.  Big thoughts were the Prince's; and it was always with a shake of his head that he considered the subjugation（征服） of the world to the arbitrary measures of Time. 
